canonical:
  title: 憶弟
  author: 卞仲良
  language: lzh
  text: 海郡驚時變無端涕在衫江雲白勝雪春水碧於藍歸夢萱堂北孤蹤竹嶺南監丞安穩未相憶正難堪
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 憶弟
  author: 卞仲良
  language: lzh
  text: 海郡驚時變。無端涕在衫。江雲白勝雪。春水碧於藍。歸夢萱堂北。孤蹤竹嶺南。監丞安穩未。相憶正難堪。
korean:
  title: 억제
  author: 변중량
  language: kor
  text: |-
    바닷 고을에서 철이 변하는 것을 놀래고
    까닭 없는 눈물이 적삼을 적시네
    강 구름은 희기가 눈보다도 더한데
    봄물은 쪽빛보다도 더 푸르구나
    돌아가고픈 마음은 훤당의 북쪽
    외로운 종 신세는 죽령 남쪽이어라
    감승이 편안한지
    생각하는 마음 견딜 수 없네
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0130_010_0520&viewSync=OT
english:
  title: Remembering My Brother
  author: Byeon Jung-ryang
  language: eng
  text: |-
    The coastal province trembles with the season's turn—
    without reason, tears soak through my robe.
    The river clouds glow whiter than snow,
    spring waters shimmer greener than indigo.

    My longing to return drifts north of the hall,
    my solitary wandering lingers south of the mountain pass.
    Is the monitor commissioner at peace?
    Missing you becomes unbearable.
  footnotes:
    - 'Xuantang (萱堂): a poetic reference to the mother''s chambers, suggesting the family home and childhood memories'
    - 'Bamboo Ridge (竹嶺): likely Jungryeong Pass, a historical mountain crossing that symbolizes separation and distance between the speaker and their brother'
